| align="left" | D4A-MIT
| The Defense4All generic mitigation driver that will enable using Defense4All even without a dedicated mitigation device by supporting redirection of suspicious traffic to any port in the controlled network. Packets will be redirected unchanged, hence the device connected to the "redirection target port" is responsible for any further processing of packets, including reinsertion into the network.
