| Tentative deliverable: Extend the Defense4All functionality beyond a single switch (as in Hydrogen) to general topologies supported/controlled by a single controller. This deliverable depends on the availability and capabilities of a network abstraction such as Group Based Policy/Affinity/Service Chaining Service. 
